AppleQEMUGuestAgent(8) System Manager's Manual AppleQEMUGuestAgent(8)

NAME

AppleQEMUGuestAgent —
implements support for QMP commands and events.

DESCRIPTION

The AppleQEMUGuestAgent daemon works only within the context of a launchd job and should not be run from the command line.
June 12, 2018 Mac OS X
